casebody.data:
Mark J. STICKLER, Respondent,
v.
Rachelle R. STICKLER, Appellant. WD 81529 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: February 19, 2019 Daniel Schramm, Chesterfield, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Michael Hanna, Raytown, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division One: Cynthia L. Martin, P.J., Victor C. Howard, and Thomas H. Newton, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Ms. Rachelle R. Stickler appeals the dissolution judgment entered by the Jackson County Circuit Court making child-custody and property-distribution awards to her and her ex-husband Mr. Mark J. Stickler. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
